quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  18,21,"Ko nii Men yaltiniri fii ma…ď…ďe, fii yo …ďe anndu pellet, Fodoore Alla nden ko nde Goonga, Pellet, Darngal ngal sikke alaa e maggal. Tuma nde …ďe poo…óondiraynoo hakkunde ma…ď…ďe fiyaake ma…ď…ďe …óen, …ďe wi'i: \"Mahee e hoore ma…ď…ďe maadi, ko Joomi ma…ď…ďe woni Anndu…óo fii Ma…ď…ďe.\" ∆Āen foolu…ďe e fiyaake mu'un wi'i: \"Men jogitoto e dow ma…ď…ďe Juulirde"
  18,22,"Aray …ďe wi'a: \"Ko …ďe tato naya…ďo ma…ď…ďe ko rawaandu ma…ď…ďe ndun.\" ∆Āe wi'a kadi: \"Ko …ďe njowo njeega…ďo ma…ď…ďe ko rawaandu ma…ď…ďe ndun ko fampaangol ka ni…ďe.\" ∆Āe wi'a kadi: \"Ko …ďe njee…ói…óo njeetata…ďo ma…ď…ďe ko rawaandu ma…ď…ďe ndun.\" Maaku: \"Ko Joomi an woni Anndu…óo limoore ma…ď…ďe, anndaa …ďe si wanaa see…óaa…ďe.\" Wata a wennju fii ma…ď…ďe si wanaa yewtere fee√Īunde, wata a lanndo fii ma…ď…ďe hay e gooto e ma…ď…ďe"
  18,23,"Wata a wi'an huunde: \"Min mi wa…óay …óun janngo"
  18,24,"Si wanaa si Alla Muuyii, janto Joomi maa…óa si a yejjitii, maaku: \"No tijjaa nde Joomi an Fewnan mi ko …ďuri …ďadaade immorde e …óun Peewal"
  18,25,"∆Āe √Īii…ďi ka fammeere ma…ď…ďe duu…ďi teeme…ó…óe tati, …ďe …ďeydi jeenay"
  18,26,"Maaku: \"Ko Alla woni Anndu…óo emmbere ko …ďe √Īii…ďi, ko Kanko heeranii ko wirnii kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi kaawes ko yi'iri wa Makko e ko naniri, alanaa …ďe gaanin Makko gi…óo, O kafidaa ka √Ďaawoore Makko hay e gooto"
  18,27,"Janngu ko wahayinaa e maa…óa kon immorde e Deftere Joomi maa nden, alaa wattitoowo Daaluyeeji=konngudi Makko …óin, a he…ďataa gaanin Makko fattorde"
